Uses of Package
org.jsonurl.factory

  • Packages that use org.jsonurl.factory 
    Package Description
    org.jsonurl.factory
    Defines generic value factory and parser interfaces, and provides a parser implementation built on the JsonUrlIterator interface.
    org.jsonurl.j2se
    A JSON→URL parser and text generator based J2SE datatypes.
    org.jsonurl.jsonorg
    A JSON→URL parser and text generator based on Douglas Crockford's original Java implementation of JSON.
    org.jsonurl.jsonp
    A JSON→URL parser and text generator based on the JSON-P interface defined by JSR-374.
  • Classes in org.jsonurl.factory used by org.jsonurl.factory 
    Class and Description
    MissingValueProvider
    A functional interface that provides a value for the given key.
    Parser
    A JSON→URL text parser.
    Parser.TransparentBuilder
    A Parser whose array builder is the same type as its array and object builder is the same type as its object.
    ValueFactory
    A ValueFactory allows Parser to be implementation independent.
    ValueFactoryParser
    Concrete implementation of Parser.
